                                                                <div role="main"><span id="maincontent"></span><h2>Practical Course Wiki</h2><div id="intro" class="box generalbox"><div class="no-overflow"><p>This wiki is to share iformation and fixes each group uses for the cars.<br></p></div></div><div class="tabtree"><ul class="tabrow0"><li class="first onerow here selected"><a class="nolink moodle-has-zindex"><span>Anzeigen</span></a><div class="tabrow2 empty">&nbsp;</div></li><li class=""><a title="Bearbeiten" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/edit.php?pageid=2384"><span>Bearbeiten</span></a></li><li class=""><a title="Kommentare" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/comments.php?pageid=2384"><span>Kommentare</span></a></li><li class=""><a title="Verlauf" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/history.php?pageid=2384"><span>Verlauf</span></a></li><li class=""><a title="Spezialseiten" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/map.php?pageid=2384"><span>Spezialseiten</span></a></li><li class="last"><a title="Dateien" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/files.php?pageid=2384"><span>Dateien</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="clearer"> </div><div class="wiki_right"><a class="printicon" href="https://www.moodle.tum.de/mod/wiki/prettyview.php?pageid=2384" id="action_link556b19857eb994">Druckversion</a></div><div class="wiki_headingtitle"><h3>Autonomous TAS Car</h3></div><div class="box generalbox"><div class="no-overflow"><div class="text_to_html"><div class="wiki-toc"><p class="wiki-toc-title">Inhaltsübersicht</p><p class="wiki-toc-section-1 wiki-toc-section">1. <a href="#toc-1">Hardware </a><a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Hardware" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">1.1. <a href="#toc-2">Wii Remotes not connecting</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-1 wiki-toc-section">2. <a href="#toc-3">Software </a><a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Software" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">2.1. <a href="#toc-4">Config Files of Move Base</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">2.2. <a href="#toc-5">Odometry model parameters for the AMCL package:</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">2.3. <a href="#toc-6">How to use RVIZ on an remote computer</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-1 wiki-toc-section">3. <a href="#toc-7">Misc. </a><a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Misc." class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">3.1. <a href="#toc-8">This is a subheader</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-1 wiki-toc-section">4. <a href="#toc-9">Networking </a><a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Networking" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></p><p class="wiki-toc-section-2 wiki-toc-section">4.1. <a href="#toc-10">This is a subheader</a></p></div><h1><a name="toc-1"></a>Hardware <a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Hardware" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></h1><h2><a name="toc-2"></a>Wii Remotes not connecting</h2><p>If the wii remotes do not connect, please press the RED sync buttong near the batteries on the wii while running hardware.launch</p><h1><a name="toc-3"></a>Software <a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Software" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></h1><h2><a name="toc-4"></a>Config Files of Move Base</h2><p>A recent known issue was that the car was not going around the corners and was constantly bumping into the wall, etc.. <br />
There was an issue with the config files that is now resolved. <br />
Please find the newest issue in the following link:  <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/zn41h5p1s43fr6t/move_base.zip?dl=0">https://www.dropbox.com/s/zn41h5p1s43fr6t/move_base.zip?dl=0</a></p><p>Please update the files in your repo accordingly : /tas/launch/config/move_base</p><h2><a name="toc-5"></a>Odometry model parameters for the AMCL package:</h2><p>Please afjust the AMCL parameters to the following (these are not the best parameters but they seem to make the model work better... please adjust them more accordingly): </p><p>!-- Odometry model parameters--&gt;</p><p>param name="odom_model_type" value="diff"/&gt;</p><p>param name="odom_alpha1" value="1.0"/&gt;</p><p>param name="odom_alpha2" value="0.2"/&gt;</p><p>param name="odom_alpha3" value="1.0"/&gt;</p><p>param name="odom_alpha4" value="0.5"/&gt;</p><h2><a name="toc-6"></a>How to use RVIZ on an remote computer</h2><p><em>Configuration Example</em><br /> Name of your robot: robot <br /> Name of your computer: thinkpad</p><p><strong>Edit the scripts</strong></p><p><em>1. Step: Change into the shell_scripts folder of the tas project </em><br /> ~/catkin_ws/src/tas_car/tas/shell_scripts</p><p><em>2. Step: Edit the file rviz_ext </em><br /> export ROS_HOSTNAME=name-of-the-robot <br /> export ROS_MASTER_URI=<a href="http://name-of-the-robot:11311">http://name-of-the-robot:11311</a></p><p>--&gt; In this case: <br /> export ROS_HOSTNAME=robot <br /> export ROS_MASTER_URI=<a href="http://robot:11311">http://robot:11311</a></p><p><em>3. Step: Edit the file rviz_ext_client </em><br /> export ROS_HOSTNAME=name-of-the-remote-computer <br /> export ROS_MASTER_URI=<a href="http://name-of-the-robot:11311">http://name-of-the-robot:11311</a></p><p>--&gt; In this case: <br /> export ROS_HOSTNAME=thinkpad <br /> export ROS_MASTER_URI=<a href="http://robot:11311">http://robot:11311</a></p><p><strong>Running the scripts</strong></p><p><em>1. Step: Run all the necessary launch files on the robot</em></p><p><em>2. Step: source the rviz_ext script on the robot</em><br /> source rviz_ext</p><p><em>3. Step: source the rviz_ext_client script on the remote computer</em><br /> source rviz_ext_client</p><p>Now, RIZV should open on the remote computer and visualize the data from the robot. </p><h1><a name="toc-7"></a>Misc. <a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Misc." class="wiki_edit_section"></a><a href="Bearbeiten">Bearbeiten</a></h1><h2><a name="toc-8"></a>This is a subheader</h2><h1><a name="toc-9"></a>Networking <a href="edit.php?pageid=2384&amp;section=Networking" class="wiki_edit_section">[Bearbeiten]</a></h1><h2><a name="toc-10"></a>This is a subheader</h2> </div></div></div><div class="wiki-tags"><span class="wiki-tags-title">Schlagworte: </span></div></div>                                <!---->
